WEBVTT

00:02.102 --> 00:04.570
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:04.604 --> 00:07.806
         (phone rings)          

00:09.342 --> 00:11.777
        Cheers.                 

00:11.811 --> 00:14.580
Uh, hang on a second,           
I'll check.                     

00:16.716 --> 00:18.884
    Yeah, the refrigerator's    
            running.            

00:18.918 --> 00:21.320
     Thank you for asking.      

00:23.590 --> 00:25.157
             What?              

00:25.191 --> 00:26.158
        (chuckles)              

00:26.192 --> 00:28.394
How could it possibly get away? 

00:30.096 --> 00:33.699
No, a refrigerator doesn't have 
     the power of movement.     

00:35.301 --> 00:38.070
  Well, yeah, sure, I get it,   
            but see,            

00:38.138 --> 00:42.041
running-- the way you're using  
it-- c-can only mean working.   

00:42.075 --> 00:44.076
         See, it's a--          
  it's what we call a homonym.  

00:46.079 --> 00:48.547
I'm sorry, too.                 

00:49.649 --> 00:52.718
Boy, Mr. Peterson,              
some people.                    

00:52.752 --> 00:54.453
(whistles)                      

00:54.521 --> 00:56.889
              Well, you tried to
            explain the joke.   

00:56.923 --> 00:58.991
      That's the problem.       

00:59.025 --> 01:00.959
      (theme song begins)       

01:05.098 --> 01:07.399
    ¶ Making your way           
      in the world today ¶      

01:07.434 --> 01:10.602
¶ Takes everything you've got ¶ 

01:10.637 --> 01:13.272
        ¶ Taking a break        
    from all your worries ¶     

01:13.306 --> 01:16.742
¶ Sure would help a lot ¶       

01:16.776 --> 01:20.612
      ¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶         

01:21.715 --> 01:24.183
  ¶ Sometimes you want to go ¶  

01:24.217 --> 01:28.654
    ¶ Where everybody           
    knows your name ¶           

01:29.956 --> 01:34.593
      ¶ And they're always      
        glad you came ¶         

01:34.627 --> 01:36.862
         ¶ You wanna be         
      where you can see ¶       

01:36.896 --> 01:39.431
         ¶ Our troubles         
    are all the same ¶          

01:39.466 --> 01:43.669
      ¶ You wanna be where      
  everybody knows your name ¶   

01:44.938 --> 01:46.905
         ¶ You wanna go         
      where people know ¶       

01:46.940 --> 01:50.142
  ¶ People are all the same ¶   

01:50.176 --> 01:54.747
      ¶ You wanna go where      
  everybody knows your name. ¶  

